om/question/455536642"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8bruvuWSwvBcEAMaCDYzNTEwMTY1IOf59oMGMAU4hQFAJnIJNDU1NTM2NjQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1618978225.9880083", "card_id": "Q_455438361", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "怎么看待日本将于 9 月份 -11 月份之间，在日本九州地区举行大规模军演？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "根据日本当地新闻 NHK 的相关报道，日本陆上自卫队计划在今年的 9 月份 -11 月份之间，在日本九州地区举行大规模军事演习。并且，日本自卫队方面不再遮遮掩掩，明确坦言此次大规模军事演习，主要是为了应对中国对日本西南地区可能的「入侵」。你怎么看待这次军演？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-2e07513571bfad1b168d2b904eb8d650_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "142 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/455438361"}}, "attached_info": "ClQI8bruvuWSwvBcEAMaCDYzNDg4MjU4IIXV9IMGMAA4UEAncgk0NTU0MzgzNjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1618978225.9885087", "card_id": "Q_453445712", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 47}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "张哲瀚后续发展会是怎样的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-dbede9c5f8a6586f5dbd6336523d8f06_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "125 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/453445712"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I8bruvuWSwvBcEAMaCDYzMDQ1MzA5INqKt4MGMAI4O0Aocgk0NTM0NDU3MTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_1618978225.988801", "card_id": "Q_455431114", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1007}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "大 LOGO 等多名博主删除炫富视频并道歉，如何看待「199 万坐月子」等炫富类视频？会带来哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，短视频平台「炫富」视频成风，花 75000 元住一晚「总统套房」，花 199 万元「坐月子」等炫富视频层出不穷，引发争议的同时，被新华社等央媒进行批评。4 月 17 日以来，多名视频博主纷纷删除「炫富」视频并道歉。记者搜索博主「大 LOGO 」后发现，短视频平台出现「请理性消费，建立健康消费观」的温馨提示。4 月 18 日，记者获悉，涉事网红主播大 LOGO 发布视频，回应称为当初的考虑不周道歉，并表示「今后会更加谨慎地选择视频题材」。 在此之前，针对短视频平台炫富的批评已经有不少，前不久小红书还重点治理了炫富类视频，共封禁账号 2371 个。 为何短视频平台上会出现如此的炫富博主，无非就是有利可图。首先打造炫富的「人设」很是容易，可以轻易的模仿他人。其次凭借炫富的方式能很快的吸引网友的好奇心。最为重要的是，炫富视频内容很容易过审，又能轻松吸引他人的关注。在拥有了庞大的粉丝群体后，可以通过带货、广告等形式「变现」，在很多炫富的视频的最后都会插入卖车、卖房或是卖表等商品广告。 有网友对网红主播「大 LOGO 吃垮北京」做过初略的统计。大 LOGO228 条视频一共花了 1327851 元，收入 7480 万。从中不难看出，这份生意经是多么的赚钱。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-4648caa305bf36e2790d2ba24c823186_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "123 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/455431114"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8bruvuWSwvBcEAMaCDYzNDg2NjM0IJ3E9IMGMGI45BlAKXIJNDU1NDMxMTE0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1618978225.9894166", "card_id": "Q_404045451", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 79}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "研究生期间为了奖学金而发一些水刊，普刊有必要吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-593ca548defea7e321f2a23dc216c03f_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "117 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/404045451"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8bruvuWSwvBcEAMaCDUyMDY2MTE3IMfP5fcFMAA4gQNAKnIJNDA0MDQ1NDUxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1618978225.9897573", "card_id": "Q_313158579", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 6782}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果用一句诗来公布恋情，你会用哪句？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b4f0fca49cb14e36d6cd90f2e1989d75_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "116 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/313158579"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI8bruvuWSwvBcEAMaCDM